Package com.telenav.kivakit.kernel.language.collections.set

Class BaseSet<Element>

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.kivakit.kernel.language.collections.set.BaseSet<Element>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Addable<Element>, Countable, Sized, NewInstance<BaseSet<Element>>, AsString, Iterable<Element>, Collection<Element>, Set<Element>
Direct Known Subclasses:
ObjectSet
public abstract class BaseSet<Element> extends Object implements Set<Element>, NewInstance<BaseSet<Element>>, Sized, Addable<Element>, AsString
A set with a maximum size. Adds the methods matching(Matcher) and first() to the usual Set operations.
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
